title: [Shartoose's Outfitting]
[Shartoose's General Store]
[Shartoose's Weaponry]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the textured red silk walls.  A iron-bound ebonwood chest and a gold-veined black marble counter sit in opposite corners while a carved ivory lighthouse rests on a plain cherrywood floor.
